The paper proposes a new mechanism to improve the energy efficiency of CNN accelerators by reducing the refresh overhead of DRAM. This topic is related to computer architecture (cs.AR), system-level design and implementation (cs.SY), energy-efficient computing (cs.ET), memory systems (cs.DC), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
